Flask-mail provides simple integration using Lamson.

Full Lamson docs here:

http://lamsonproject.org/

Sample usage:

from flask import Flask
from flaskext.mail import init_mail, relay, MailResponse

app = Flask(__name__)
init_mail(app)

@app.route("/")
def index():
    msg = MailResponse(Subject="hello",
                       From="me@here.com",
                       To=["you@there.com"])

    msg.Body = "hello"
    msg.Html = "<b>hello</b>"
    relay.deliver(msg)




